<template>
  <v-app id="inspire">
    <v-main>

         
 <v-row style="margin-top: 2%; max-height: 2%;  background-color:pink">
        <Header style="max-height: -webkit-fill-available; margin-left: 9%" />
      </v-row>

     
        <v-row>
          <v-col>
            <v-list v-for="(data, x) in filteredData" :key="x + 1">
              <v-list-item>
                <v-list-item-icon>
                  <v-icon color="indigo"> mdi-map-marker </v-icon>
                </v-list-item-icon>

                <v-list-item-content>
                  <v-list-item-title>{{ data.name }}</v-list-item-title>
                  <v-list-item-subtitle>
                    {{ data.city }} - {{ data.country }}</v-list-item-subtitle
                  >
                </v-list-item-content>
              </v-list-item>
              <v-divider inset></v-divider>
            </v-list>
          </v-col>
        </v-row>

    </v-main>
  </v-app>
</template>

<script>
import axios from "axios";
import Header from "./components/Header.vue";

export default {
  /* eslint-disable */
  // eslint-disable-next-line
  name: "Home",
components: {
    Header,
  },
  data: () => ({
    searchString: "",
    postList: [],
  }),
  methods: {
    getData() {
      axios.get("mockData.json").then((response) => {
        const list = response.data.data;
        for (let i = 0; i < list.length; i++) {
          const x = list[i];

          this.postList.push({
            name: x[0],
            company: x[1],
            email: x[2],
            date: x[3],
            country: x[4],
            city: x[5],
          });
        }
        // class Post {
        //   constructor(title, link, author, img) {
        //     this.title = title;
        //     this.link = link;
        //     this.author = author;
        //     this.img = img;
        //   }
        // }
      });
    },
  },
  computed: {
    filteredData() {
      var self = this;

      // if (!self.searchString) {
      //   return (searchData = "Aran覺lan bulunamad覺");
      // }

      // self.searchString = self.searchString.trim().toLowerCase();

      // self.postList = self.postList.filter((item) => {
      //   if (item.name.toLowerCase().indexOf(self.searchString) !== -1) {
      //     return item;
      //   }
      // });

      // this.postList = self.postList;

      // return self.postList;

      // return postList.filter((post) => {
      //   return post.name.toLowerCase().includes(searchString.toLowerCase());
      // });

      self.postList = self.postList.filter((customer) => {
        if (
          customer.name
            .toLowerCase()
            .indexOf(self.searchString.toLowerCase()) >= 0 ||
          customer.company
            .toLowerCase()
            .indexOf(self.searchString.toLowerCase()) >= 0 ||
          customer.city
            .toLowerCase()
            .indexOf(self.searchString.toLowerCase()) >= 0
        )
          return customer;
      });
      return self.postList;
    },
  },
  created() {
    console.log("-----------++++");
    axios.get("mockData.json").then((response) => {
      const list = response.data.data;
      for (let i = 0; i < list.length; i++) {
        const x = list[i];

        this.postList.push({
          name: x[0],
          company: x[1],
          email: x[2],
          date: x[3],
          country: x[4],
          city: x[5],
        });
      }
    });
  },
};
</script>
